en.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/M%E1%BA%A1ch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tang/poem-d91Qb5A1bVzWJzHXW77qWg">Mạch thượng tang - 陌上桑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%A1t-Li%E1%BB%85u/poem-xdpmxMrS5eWC5GOr-k4MCg">Tần Cát Liễu - 秦吉了</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-Ho%C3%A0nh/Th%C3%A1nh-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-HXEYqappREcELY9L8exshA">Thánh Ân tự - 聖恩寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-Ho%C3%A0nh/author-4o944Mvy28lwY4v7WA7VOw">Trần Bích Hoành</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Xu%C3%A2n-hi%E1%BB%83u/poem-cZRx4GRlCqEeB8CMkMoCzQ">Xuân hiểu - 春曉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
